726458f-a.title: Queens: Cypress Avenue - Hancock Street
726458f-a.text:
Cypress Ave. (tracks thereon), west of Hancock Street, showing in the foreground an old hotel (white) operated by the following owners: one Beck, 1860. (He erected it in 1859 on land purchased of Nicholas Wyckoff.); Stroebel, in 1873; and one Kreuscher, from 1880-1912.
1922.
View 2: April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
